{"info": {"author": "Trim21", "author_email": "i@trim21.me", "bugtrack_url": null, "classifiers": ["Programming Language :: Python :: 3", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.5", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.6", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.7"], "description": "# Read Python3 Source File With Correct Encoding\n\naccording to <https://www.python.org/dev/peps/pep-0263/>,\npython3 source file encoding are default to be `utf-8`.\n\nBut `open()`'s encoding will be `gbk` on windows,\nSo don't use `open` without encoding to read a python3 source file. \n\n\nexample:\n\n```python\nfrom read_source import get_encoding, read\nprint(get_encoding('tests/source/gb18030/dash-star-dash.py')) # gb18030\nwith read('tests/source/gb18030/dash-star-dash.py') as f:\n    print(f.read()) \n    # -*- coding: gb18030 -*-\n```", "description_content_type": "text/markdown", "docs_url": null, "download_url": "", "downloads": {"last_day": -1, "last_month": -1, "last_week": -1}, "home_page": "", "keywords": "", "license": "", "maintainer": "Trim21", "maintainer_email": "i@trim21.me", "name": "read-source", "package_url": "https://pypi.org/project/read-source/", "platform": "", "project_url": "https://pypi.org/project/read-source/", "project_urls": null, "release_url": "https://pypi.org/project/read-source/0.0.2/", "requires_dist": null, "requires_python": ">=3.5,<4.0", "summary": "", "version": "0.0.2", "yanked": false, "html_description": "<div class=\"project-description\">\n            <h1>Read Python3 Source File With Correct Encoding</h1>\n<p>according to <a href=\"https://www.python.org/dev/peps/pep-0263/\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://www.python.org/dev/peps/pep-0263/</a>,\npython3 source file encoding are default to be <code>utf-8</code>.</p>\n<p>But <code>open()</code>'s encoding will be <code>gbk</code> on windows,\nSo don't use <code>open</code> without encoding to read a python3 source file.</p>\n<p>example:</p>\n<pre><span class=\"kn\">from</span> <span class=\"nn\">read_source</span> <span class=\"kn\">import</span> <span class=\"n\">get_encoding</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">read</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">print</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">get_encoding</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s1\">'tests/source/gb18030/dash-star-dash.py'</span><span class=\"p\">))</span> <span class=\"c1\"># gb18030</span>\n<span class=\"k\">with</span> <span class=\"n\">read</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s1\">'tests/source/gb18030/dash-star-dash.py'</span><span class=\"p\">)</span> <span class=\"k\">as</span> <span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"p\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"nb\">print</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">read</span><span class=\"p\">())</span> \n    <span class=\"c1\"># -*- coding: gb18030 -*-</span>\n</pre>\n\n          </div>"}, "last_serial": 6174807, "releases": {"0.0.1": [{"comment_text": "", "digests": {"md5": "e3ddd2df0bf260c57706e482d12d9d73", "sha256": "7dbc5643ff60edc39950951043c2f4bc1aa4995ea6db0ec497f5ef7df7a9eedd"}, "downloads": -1, "filename": "read_source-0.0.1-py3-none-any.whl", "has_sig": false, "md5_digest": "e3ddd2df0bf260c57706e482d12d9d73", "packagetype": "bdist_wheel", "python_version": "py3", "requires_python": ">=3.5,<4.0", "size": 1219, "upload_time": "2019-11-21T12:02:39", "upload_time_iso_8601": "2019-11-21T12:02:39.670583Z", "url": "https://files.pythonhosted.org/packages/bd/e5/04191201aad632656febcdf76bd02fdedd9ca3639a29459f480a91aaf829/read_source-0.0.1-py3-none-any.whl", "yanked": false}, {"comment_text": "", "digests": {"md5": "152d5dc33c0ab39551fbbb8eeabb8003", "sha256": "0454cc6de165d9b1b123f0b5e7fc0edd90fd2361ae656e4cde76bd1e978a68cb"}, "downloads": -1, "filename": "read_source-0.0.1.tar.gz", "has_sig": false, "md5_digest": "152d5dc33c0ab39551fbbb8eeabb8003", "packagetype": "sdist", "python_version": "source", "requires_python": ">=3.5,<4.0", "size": 959, "uploa